<!-- fwtable fwsrc="未命名" fwbase="sr.jpg" fwstyle="Dreamweaver" fwdocid = "1344182167" fwnested="1" -->
  <tr><!-- row 1 -->
    <td align="right" valign="top">
    
		<!--标题开始-->
	      <div style="font-family:'华文行楷'; font-size:18pt;  color:#411500; text-align:center; padding-top:15px;">
	      	“皱面还丹”是道家对人参的称谓
	      </div>
	      <!-- 副标题 -->
	      <div style="font-family:'华文行楷'; font-size:16pt;  color:#411500; text-align:center; padding-top:15px;">
	      	
	      </div>
	      <!--标题结束-->
		<div style="text-align:center"><a name="1" id="1"></a>
		<img name="sr_r3_c1" src="images/sr_r3_c1.gif" width="293" height="32" border="0" id="sr_r3_c1" alt="" /></div>
		<!--图片-->
		
		<!--图片结束-->
		<!-- 作者 -->
		
			<div style="font-family:'宋体'; font-size:12pt;  color:#411500; text-align:center;padding-bottom:8px;">
		      	
		    </div>
		
	   <div style="text-align:left; color:#88510c; font-size:14px; line-height:20px; width:900px; height:auto; margin:0 auto;">
	   		<!-- 显示内容 -->
	   		<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">孙文采</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;人参的别名雅号极其繁多，明代著名医家李时珍在《本草纲目》一书中将人微、人衔、鬼盖、黄参、血参、土精、地精、神草等八个别名分别加以诠释，但他对唐代侯宁极《药谱》一书中的&ldquo;人参别名皱面还丹&rdquo;却未解只字。笔者翻经查典也未查到，日前偶读道书，有所顿悟，不揣冒昧，草率为文，就教于学界。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;笔者认为，&ldquo;皱面还丹&rdquo;，为中国道家对人参的称谓。其理由如下<font face="Times New Roman">:</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;道教的根本信仰是长生不死，得道成仙。所谓&ldquo;道&rdquo;，即灵而有性的&ldquo;神异之物&rdquo;。这个&ldquo;神异之物&rdquo;便是九丹<font face="Times New Roman">:</font><font face="宋体">丹华、神符丹、还丹、神丹、饵丹、炼丹、柔丹、伏丹、塞丹。另有小还丹、大还丹、金液还丹、玉液还丹等。九丹&ldquo;为长生之要，得一丹便仙&rdquo;。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;《抱朴子&middot;金丹篇》<font face="Times New Roman">:</font><font face="宋体">&ldquo;一转之丹，服之三年得仙，二转之丹，服之二年得仙，三转之丹，服之一年得仙，四转之丹，服之半年得仙，五转之丹，服之百日得仙，六转之丹，服之四十日得仙，七转之丹，服之三十日得仙</font><font face="Times New Roman">;</font><font face="宋体">八转之丹，服之十日得仙</font><font face="Times New Roman">;</font><font face="宋体">九转之丹服之三日得仙。&rdquo;</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;以九转之丹再炼，化为还丹即为金丹。道教认为，金丹烧炼时间愈久，反复次数愈多，药力愈足，服后成仙愈速，且以九转为贵。道家自称服金丹可白日升天。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;九转即九还，九为金，九还即金还，&ldquo;所以还返归居之名者，即是后天复先天之义&rdquo;。&ldquo;还&rdquo;有反归之义。《抱朴子&middot;金丹篇》<font face="Times New Roman">:</font><font face="宋体">&ldquo;丹砂烧之成水银，积变又还成丹砂。&rdquo;意思说，使丹砂烧成水银，积存久了又还原为丹砂。用现代化学语言讲，因水银经氧化而成红色的氧化物，又同于原来丹砂之色，因以为还丹也。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;丹者，山石之精，故凡药物之精者日丹。金丹，古代方士、道士用黄金在炉鼎中炼成&ldquo;玉液&rdquo;，或用铅汞等八石烧炼成黄色的药金<font face="Times New Roman">(</font><font face="宋体">还丹</font><font face="Times New Roman">)</font><font face="宋体">，故名。道家认为，服金丹可以长生不老，即谓吃后可以成仙。《抱朴子&middot;金丹篇》</font><font face="Times New Roman">:</font><font face="宋体">&ldquo;夫金丹之为物，烧之愈久，变化愈妙</font><font face="Times New Roman">;</font><font face="宋体">黄金入火，百炼不消，埋之毕天不朽。服此二药，烧人身体，故能令人不老不死。&rdquo;</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;唐宋以前，金丹是指炼外丹。宋金以后，则指修内丹。宋张伯端《悟真篇》<font face="Times New Roman">:</font><font face="宋体">&ldquo;学仙须是学天仙，唯有金丹最的端。&rdquo;《悟真外篇</font><font face="Times New Roman">.</font><font face="宋体">金丹四百字并序》</font><font face="Times New Roman">:</font><font face="宋体">&ldquo;七返九</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">还金液大丹者，七乃火数，九乃金数，以炼金，返本还元，谓之金丹也。&rdquo;所论均指内丹，借用外丹炉鼎丹砂铅汞之名，详述抱一守中，炼元养素，修心养性，炼精、气、神。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;总之，还丹<font face="Times New Roman">(</font><font face="宋体">金丹</font><font face="Times New Roman">)</font><font face="宋体">有&ldquo;反还之功&rdquo;，&ldquo;能令者者返壮，死者复活，枯者即荣&rdquo;。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">(<font face="宋体">《宗教词典》</font><font face="Times New Roman">488</font><font face="宋体">贞</font><font face="Times New Roman">)</font><font face="宋体">正如梁王符《东南射山》诗曰</font><font face="Times New Roman">:</font><font face="宋体">&ldquo;还丹改客质，握髓驻流年。&rdquo;但是，历史已证明，还丹不能&ldquo;令人不老不死&rdquo;，更不能&ldquo;令死者父活&rdquo;，无需多所赘述。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;《本草乘雅半偈》<font face="Times New Roman">:</font><font face="宋体">&ldquo;先人云</font><font face="Times New Roman">:</font><font face="宋体">参赞天地，奠安神理，精腴在握，还丹可期，形山之秘室，帝王之仁泽也。&rdquo;&ldquo;功魁群草，力等丹丸矣。&rdquo;显然，在这里人参与还丹联系起来了。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;的确，人参也有&ldquo;反还之功&rdquo;，也能令&ldquo;老者返壮&rdquo;或&ldquo;返本还元&rdquo;之功能，换言之，人参有&ldquo;适应原样&rdquo;的作用。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;《临江县志》曰<font face="Times New Roman">:</font><font face="宋体">人参&ldquo;设被野兽践踏，或荒火焚烧即数年不出土，俗云&lsquo;睡</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">觉&rsquo;。再出土时仍由初生之二荚子、灯台子继续长至六匹叶为止，以故人参富有起死回生、返老还童之能力。&rdquo;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;这里的&ldquo;起死回生、返老还童&rdquo;与前文的&ldquo;老者返壮、返本还元&rdquo;，是同义的。不仅如此，在唐杜光庭《神仙感遇传》一书中还记有老叟服食千年人参白日升天的故事。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;笔者遥想当年的道教高功据人参有&ldquo;返还之功&rdquo;而命名人参为&ldquo;还丹&rdquo;，这也是对人参的高度评价，深入的认识。为了与道教诸丹相区别，不再称世俗名字，因此给人参命名为&ldquo;皱面还丹&rdquo;这个&ldquo;道号&rdquo;。而&ldquo;皱面&rdquo;之义，似乎是描绘人参干燥根的表皮如&ldquo;皱纹重叠的面&rdquo;。人参取名皱面还丹，可跻身于诸种丹药之行列中。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;此文为笔者的大胆推测，恳望取得学界的共识。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<!--EndFragment-->
	   </div>
	   <div style="text-align:left; color:#88510c; font-size:14px; line-height:20px; width:900px; height:auto; margin:0 auto;">
	   		<!-- 附件 -->
	   		
		   		
			
	   </div>
   
   
   </td>
